</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[85,1147,1556,1590]" pageId="140" pageNumber="741" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="140.[84,1290,1083,1708]" box="[85,1147,1556,1590]" pageId="140" pageNumber="741">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[85,320,1556,1590]" pageId="140" pageNumber="741">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Cheesman’s Vlei Rat is presumably diurnal or crepuscular.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
